  \begin {tikzcd}
    x\ar [dr, "\iota _x"']\ar [rr, equals] && x \\
    & x\oplus  y\ar [ur, "\pi _x"']\ar [dr, "\pi _y"] \\
    y\ar [ur, "\iota _y"]\ar [rr, equals] && y
  \end {tikzcd}
  \quad \text { and }\quad 
  \begin {tikzcd}
    x\ar [dr, "\iota _x"']\ar [rr, "0"] && y \\
    & x\oplus  y\ar [ur, "\pi _y"']\ar [dr, "\pi _x"] \\
    y\ar [ur, "\iota _y"]\ar [rr, "0"'] && x
  \end {tikzcd}


 commute and the sum of
x\oplus  y\xrightarrow {\pi _x}x\xrightarrow {\iota _x} x\oplus  y\text { and }x\oplus  y\xrightarrow {\pi _y}y\xrightarrow {\iota _y} x\oplus  y is the identity 1_{x\oplus  y}.
